        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Specify the Subnet Mask</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600">The mask can be selected from the available formats using the dropdown menu:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mt-2 space-y-2 text-slate-600">
            <li>Decimal notation (e.g., <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">255.255.255.0</code>)</li>
            <li>CIDR notation (e.g., <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">/24</code>)</li>
